task.summary: Started adding location based services to the app
Initial steps done for checking if a store is nearby.
Added Google maps integration support for finding nearby instances of stores
Removed FindLocation and its references. Added an intent service for location services
Clicking on a notification brings up the ViewListDetail for that store
When within 100 meters of a location, fire off a notification!
Can now notify without opening the app
